snippet.title: Random Hands
snippet.description:
WELCOME TO RANDOM HANDS!!
"Work Hard, Stay Humble"
                -Random Hands.

Hi, as you know we do many random mechanical activities eg; we make Knives and Swords / we make variety of creative items and also we do restoration projects on our YouTube channel while using some modern techniques with basic tools. Our expertise are in casting and forging. Even we do many more random projects including metal etching / electrolysis / electroplating process (Gold plating / Cooper plating / Nickel plating / Chrome plating) several times. We love working with metals like Steel / Brass / Aluminum / Gold / Silver etc.

I am THANKFUL to you for visiting my channel. This is honor for me to share all expertise and knowledge to you.
ALL WE NEED IS YOUR LOVE  :)

IF YOU ARE A BUSINESS OWNER or whatever you are dealing with related to my field and want to sponsor or giveaway your PRODUCTS in my VIDEOS you are welcome to contact me.
Email: darkmoondarklight@gmail.com
